list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Implemented tests and test object with generic type fields.
Initially, this test was meant for wrapper classes and String fields, but it turns out to be that generic type fields itself has a unique property (type erasure) that has to be tested.

task.summary:
Constructed the basic structure of the utility class ObjectSaver.
Added fundamental features of a utility class such as final class, private constructors, static methods.
Added JavaDoc and TODOs to describe functions' purpose.

Constructed a basic JUnit test for utility class ObjectSaver.
Added the most basic test for save and load function.
The ObjectSaver utility class will be implemented through test-driven development, and ObjectSaverTest will have multiple test cases later on.

Changed the format of the save file. (YAML -> CSV)
The save function has also been changed accordingly.
This change was made to focus of the save and load functionality, rather than the parsing functionality, which can be a whole new library by itself.

Implemented load function for data type "int".
This version of implementation will assume that all fields of an object are "int", and use the "Integer.parseInt(String s)" function.
Next implementation should focus on making the load function use different parse function for different primitive types.

Implemented primitive test objects, and wrote test cases according to them.
The ObjectSaver class will be implemented through test-driven development according to the written test cases.
Next implementation should focus on making the load function use different parse function for different primitive types.

Implemented load function for primitive types
The load function works for both public and private fields.
Has been tested for all primitive types. Additionally, the save function was tested for all primitive types as well.

Implemented save and load function for String types
Since String is used as much as primitive types (and also has similar behavior), I decided to categorize it with other primitive types for testing.
Additionally, refactored existing test and test objects according to the category.
